name: Dartmouth Cycling Club
description: Road and mountain biking group. Weekly rides around the Upper Valley. All levels welcome!

name: Dartmouth A Cappella
description: Student-run a cappella group performing pop, jazz, and classical arrangements. Auditions every fall.

name: Hack Dartmouth
description: CS and engineering club organizing hackathons, coding workshops, and tech talks. Open to all majors.

name: Green Key Society
description: Community service and campus volunteer organization. Weekly volunteering at local food bank and tutoring programs.

name: Dartmouth Foodies
description: Exploring the best food spots in Hanover and the Upper Valley. Monthly restaurant crawls and cooking sessions.
